<item>
            <title>[DERBY-1491] Provide ALTER TABLE functionality to change a column&apos;s default value</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1491</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Provide a way to alter the default value for an existing column in an existing table. The syntax should probably some variant of the ALTER TABLE statement.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12345618">DERBY-1491</key>
